"adjacent":value,
"readable": value,
"empty":
}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1 +1 @@
-{ "adjacent": value, "readable": value, "empty" }
+{ "adjacent": value, "readable": value, "empty": }
```

# Output

```yml
